data.title: Icecube Records Home Page
data.text:
Partytime, first week charting

Party, party time! we are really happy at the Icecube Records crew. Markko Svensson latest single was placed in the position 16 (16,384 copies sold). We are expecting a rise.

Dervla Baker-Pryce, in September

In The Heat Of The Night is probably going to be released the second week of September and the album that will have the song at the end of the same month.

Roland charted in the position 24

The song West End Girls sold 10,729 copies in its first week.By this week Roland is going to be performing his song in some tv shows in the UK. Check your TV guide to see when he is appearing.
